{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"82d1adf75d","title":"复叶剑英、陈电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ae202cde90","index":0,"year":1949,"month":9,"day":12,"articleId":"82d1adf75d"}],"tags":[{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"5371cebd7d","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"82d1adf75d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的复叶剑英、陈康电的主要内容。"},{"id":"1bb3888228","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"82d1adf75d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"叶剑英、陈质9月8日致电中共中央军委，报告华南分局赣州会议制订的解放广东的作战方案，提出依照中央军委意图先消灭北江、东江之故，进占曲江（现属韶关币）、惠阳，创造和平解决条件，争取和平解决。同时，准备对付坚守广州顽抗之敌。因第四兵团与第十五兵团相隔过远，为求得同时展开，齐头并进，实行铅形合围，必须先行集结预定地区，9月底集结完毕。"}],"contents":[{"id":"48be3d8642","type":"title","text":"复叶剑英、陈质电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"82d1adf75d"},{"id":"5371cebd7d","type":"paragraph","text":"八日电悉。两兵团第一步集结并休息数日，第二步齐头进至曲江、翁源地区并休息数日，第三步协力夺取广州。除此以外均同意。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"82d1adf75d"}],"page":{"id":"5b34ddfb86","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"82d1adf75d","start":236,"end":236}}}},"__N_SSG":true}